## BidStrategy [/campaigns/:id/bidStrategy/:subid/?include=includes]
Get the BidStrategy that the campaign is using by ID 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Campaign to perform action with. Has example value.
    + subid (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the BidStrategy to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a BidStrategy by ID [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

